### Send SMS Verification Code
POST http://localhost:5000/api/waitlist/send-verification-code
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "user_id": "user_123",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "phone": "+573024690359",
  "extension": "ext123"
}

### Test SMS Service (Direct)
POST https://api.sendmator.com/v1/sms/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient_type": "direct_sms",
  "phone_number": "+573024690359",
  "content": "Your verification code is 123456. It expires in 5 minutes."
}

### Send SMS via Sendmator
POST https://api.sendmator.com/api/v1/otp/send
X-API-Key: sk_live_dd4da5f5e137de7d0cdce261aaa04df56dd7e3d4eb50886c39f7fff7b4f81188
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "channels": ["sms", "whatsapp"],
    "recipients": {
      "sms": "+573024690359",
      "whatsapp": "573024690359"
    },
    "metadata": {
      "purpose": "phone_verification",
      "user_id": "user_67890"
    },
    "sandbox_mode": true
}